'''謝琳·喬普拉'''（{{lang-hi|शर्लिन चोपड़ा}}，{{bd|1984年|2月11日}}）是一名印度女模特兒、演員和歌手，以在[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]的工作而聞名。2012年7月，喬普拉成為《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》雜誌上首位裸體的印度女性<ref name="Telegraph first nude">{{Cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/9426510/Bollywood-star-becomes-first-Indian-to-pose-nude-for-Playboy.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815141822/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/9426510/Bollywood-star-becomes-first-Indian-to-pose-nude-for-Playboy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title= Sherlyn Chopra shoots for Playboy |url= http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/sherlyn-chopra-shoots-for-playboy-244120 |date= 2013-07-17 |publisher= NDTV |accessdate= 2021-01-18 |archive-date= 2015-08-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150806032820/http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/sherlyn-chopra-shoots-for-playboy-244120 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sherlyn Chopra goes Naked to ride on Horseback|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/09/sherlyn-chopra-goes-naked-to-ride-on-horseback/|publisher=Bihar Prabda|date=2013-09-20|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2015-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413210613/http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/09/sherlyn-chopra-goes-naked-to-ride-on-horseback/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；照片於兩年後發布<ref name="IndiaToday(2014-08-14)">{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/sherlyn-chopras-playboy-photoshoot-pics-out-204041-2014-08-14|title=Sherlyn Chopra's Playboy photoshoot pics finally out|work=India Today|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2018-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911032139/https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/sherlyn-chopras-playboy-photoshoot-pics-out-204041-2014-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，她被選為節目《{{le|MTV Splitsvilla|MTV Splitsvilla}}》第六季主持人<ref name=":0">{{cite news|title=Sherlyn Chopra to host the sixth season of MTV Splitsvilla|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/sherlyn-chopra-to-host-the-sixth-season-of-mtv-splitsvilla/384755-44-124.html|access-date=2013-04-23|newspaper=IBN Live|date=2013-04-23|archive-date=2013-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413230653/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/sherlyn-chopra-to-host-the-sixth-season-of-mtv-splitsvilla/384755-44-124.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。喬普拉於2009年參加了真人秀《{{le|名人老大哥 (印度節目)|Bigg Boss (Hindi TV series)|名人老大哥}}》{{le|名人老大哥 (印度第三季)|Bigg Boss (Hindi season 3)|第三季}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/sherlyn-chopra-evicted-from-bigg-boss/5017/|title=Sherlyn Chopra evicted from Bigg Boss|date=2009-10-30|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2019-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324194732/https://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/sherlyn-chopra-evicted-from-bigg-boss/5017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年12月，她發行了自己的音樂單曲〈Bad Girl〉<ref>{{cite web|title=Sherlyn Chopra’s new Music Video Bad Girl goes Viral|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/01/sherlyn-chopras-news-song-bad-girl-goes-viral/|work=Biharprabha News|access-date=2014-01-04|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929053640/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/01/sherlyn-chopras-news-song-bad-girl-goes-viral/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
謝琳·喬普拉出生於[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]][[海得拉巴_(印度)|海得拉巴]]，由[[基督徒|基督徒]]父親和[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]母親扶養<ref>{{cite web|title=Sherlyn Chopra|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/sherlyn-chopra|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213101629/https://www.indiatoday.in/sherlyn-chopra|archive-date=2020-02-13|accessdate=2021-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>；父親是一名醫生<ref name=parents>{{cite web |author=Staff Reporter |date=2012-07-23 |url=http://www.emirates247.com/2.569/take-one/bollywood-insult-playboy-calls-sherlyn-chopra-a-legend-2012-07-23-1.468465 |title=Bollywood insult? Playboy calls Sherlyn Chopra a legend |publisher=emirates247.com |access-date=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116224828/http://www.emirates247.com/2.569/take-one/bollywood-insult-playboy-calls-sherlyn-chopra-a-legend-2012-07-23-1.468465 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在[[塞康德拉巴德|塞康德拉巴德]]的{{le|史丹利女子高中|Stanley Girls High School}}和聖安女子學院（Saint Ann's College for Women）就讀。1999年，她被加冕為「安得拉小姐」<ref name="photogallery.indiatimes.com" /><ref name=conf>{{cite web |author=Madhumitha |date=2008-12-18 |url=http://www.go-nxg.com/?p=3253 |title=Confessions of a diva |publisher=Go-nxg.com |access-date=2011-07-08 |archive-date=2011-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005215535/http://www.go-nxg.com/?p=3253 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

喬普拉的早期表演生涯包括在幾部[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]電影中擔任要角，如《{{le|紅卍|Red Swastik}}》（2007年）和她首部[[泰卢固电影|泰卢固电影]]《{{le|一部阿拉文電影|A Film by Aravind}}》（2005年）。<ref>{{cite web|title=A film by Aravind|url=http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-afilmbyaravind.html|work=idlebrain.com|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823103019/http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-afilmbyaravind.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年，她參加了真人秀《{{le|名人老大哥 (印度節目)|Bigg Boss (Hindi TV series)|名人老大哥}}》{{le|名人老大哥 (印度第三季)|Bigg Boss (Hindi season 3)|第三季}}成為參賽選手<ref name="autogenerated">{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tv-/Rakhis-mom-on-Bigg-Boss/articleshow/5088996.cms |title=Rakhi's mom on Bigg Boss |date=2009-10-06 |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |publisher=[[Indiatimes|Indiatimes]] |accessdate=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224211933/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tv-/Rakhis-mom-on-Bigg-Boss/articleshow/5088996.cms%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在比賽的第27天中淘汰<ref>{{cite web|url=https://photogallery.indiatimes.com/awards/filmfare-awards/55th-idea-filmfare-awards/55th-idea-filmfare-awards-red-carpet/Outrageous-Sherlyn/articleshow/5625547.cms|title=55th Idea Filmfare Awards: Red carpet|work=ETimes Photogallery|date=2010-02-27|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014075010/http://photogallery.indiatimes.com/awards/filmfare-awards/Outrageous-Sherlyn/articleshow/5625547.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。從2013年起，她在英語印度色情電影《{{le|印度性愛慾|Kamasutra 3D}}》擔任主角，並出現在[[第66屆坎城影展|第66屆坎城影展]]上放映的預告片中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Post-Playboy-stint-Sherlyn-Chopra-to-do-Kama-Sutra-in-3D/Article1-951664.aspx |title=Sherlyn Chopra to do Kama Sutra film in 3D, after Playboy stint |publisher=[[Hindustan_Times|Hindustan Times]] |date=2012-10-29 |access-date=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2013-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130210144816/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Post-Playboy-stint-Sherlyn-Chopra-to-do-Kama-Sutra-in-3D/Article1-951664.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/hindi/article/93747.html|title=Indian @ Cannes 'Kamasutra 3D' icing up the cake of 66th CIFF|publisher=indiaglitz.com|date=2013-05-17|access-date=2013-06-01|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924115326/http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/hindi/article/93747.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但之後她與{{le|盧佩許·保羅|Rupesh Paul}}發生糾紛，主因是喬普拉私自未經許可將影片拍攝的視頻片段上傳到她的YouTube頻道，之後又指控導演虐待自己；最後雙方都放棄了訴訟，公開聲明他們已決定繼續擺脫誤解<ref>{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news-and-interviews/Rupesh-Paul-and-Sherlyn-Chopra-forget-differences/articleshow/31771214.cms |title=Rupesh Paul and Sherlyn Chopra forget differences |work=The Times of India |date=2014-03-10 |accessdate=2014-04-01 |archive-date=2019-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190205112303/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news-and-interviews/Rupesh-Paul-and-Sherlyn-Chopra-forget-differences/articleshow/31771214.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年6月，她對媒體說，她不再從事該項目<ref name="Hindustan Times">{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/kamasutra-3d-is-not-my-film-sherlyn-chopra/story-rSXBHx4xqbPZhP57syZK5K.html |title=Kamasutra 3D is not my film: Sherlyn Chopra |publisher=[[Hindustan_Times|Hindustan Times]] |date=2016-08-16 |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115203103/https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/kamasutra-3d-is-not-my-film-sherlyn-chopra/story-rSXBHx4xqbPZhP57syZK5K.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

